'''塞語'''（Saka、Sakan），又稱'''東部塞語'''，是一種曾在[[塔里木盆地|塔里木盆地]][[于闐|-{于}-闐]]王國與[[圖木舒克|圖木舒克]]使用的[[塞迦|塞族]]方言，屬東[[伊朗語|伊朗語]]。<ref>榮新江：《華戎交匯：敦煌民族與中西交通》（蘭州：甘肅教育出版社，2008），頁164。</ref>在其下又分成兩種方言，在[[于闐|-{于}-闐]]使用的，稱為'''-{于}-闐語'''（Khotanese），'''-{于}-闐塞語'''和'''和闐語'''等，在圖木舒克使用的，稱'''圖木舒克語'''（Tumshuqese）。

==歷史==
這兩種方言，都源自[[斯基泰人|斯基泰人]]。汉语文献中不见该区域受到过入侵的记录，一种理论认为两支操相近方言的塞人部落约在公元前200年定居于此。<ref>{{Cite journal |last=Bailey |first=H. W. |date=1970 |title=Saka Studies: The Ancient Kingdom of Khotan |journal=Iran: Journal of the British Institute of Persian Studies |language=en |volume=8 |issue=1 |doi=10.1080/05786967.1970.11834790 |jstor=4299633}}</ref>{{rp|68}}

于阗语文本主要是7到10世纪的，也有些残卷可追溯至5或6世纪。图木舒克语的材料要少得多，难以精确定年，其中大部分可能写于7世纪晚期至8世纪。<ref>{{Cite book |last=Emmerick |first=Ronald E. |title=The Iranian Languages |date=2009 |publisher=Routledge |isbn=978-1-135-79704-1 |editor-last=Windfuhr |editor-first=Gernot |language=en |chapter=7. Khotanese and Tumshuqese |chapter-url=https://books.google.com/books?id=QtpQZ1DD6tEC&q=tumshuqese+century&pg=PA377 |access-date=2021-12-11 |archive-date=2021-08-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210814100317/https://books.google.com/books?id=QtpQZ1DD6tEC&q=tumshuqese+century&pg=PA377 |dead-url=no }}</ref>{{rp|377–415}}<ref>{{Iranica|buddhism-iii}}</ref>

塞语在突厥穆斯林[[新疆的伊斯兰化和突厥化|征服]][[于阗|于阗]]后逐步走向消亡。

在11世纪，于阗仍保持着自己的语言文字，这可能要归功于[[麻赫穆德·喀什噶里|麻赫穆德·喀什噶里]]。<ref>{{Cite journal |last=Kocaoğlu |first=Timur |date=2004 |title=Diwanu Lugatı’t-Turk and Contemporary Linguistics |url=http://journals.manas.edu.kg/mjtc/oldarchives/2004/17_781-2049-1-PB.pdf |journal=MANAS Journal of Turkic Civilization Studies |language=en |volume=1 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200519050601/http://journals.manas.edu.kg/mjtc/oldarchives/2004/17_781-2049-1-PB.pdf |archive-date=2020-05-19 |access-date=2016-08-22}}</ref>{{rp|165–169}}<ref name="LeviSela2010">{{Cite book |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=SAX5ohFkcVgC&q=yabaqu&pg=PA72 |title=Islamic Central Asia: An Anthology of Historical Sources |date=2010 |publisher=Indiana University Press |isbn=978-0-253-35385-6 |editor-last=Levi |editor-first=Scott Cameron |location=Bloomington |language=en |editor-last2=Sela |editor-first2=Ron |access-date=2021-12-11 |archive-date=2021-08-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210814100317/https://books.google.com/books?id=SAX5ohFkcVgC&q=yabaqu&pg=PA72 |dead-url=no }}</ref>{{rp|72–}}Kanchaki和[[粟特语|粟特语]]等非突厥语到11世纪仍在一些地方使用。<ref name="LeviSela2010 2">{{Cite book |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=SAX5ohFkcVgC&pg=PA72 |title=Islamic Central Asia: An Anthology of Historical Sources |date=2010 |publisher=Indiana University Press |isbn=978-0-253-35385-6 |editor-last=Levi |editor-first=Scott Cameron |language=en |editor-last2=Sela |editor-first2=Ron |access-date=2021-12-11 |archive-date=2016-01-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160101193741/https://books.google.com/books?id=SAX5ohFkcVgC&pg=PA72 |dead-url=no }}</ref>{{rp|72–}}据信Kanchaki属于塞语。<ref name="DaniLitvinsky1996">{{Cite book |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=883OZBe2sMYC&pg=PA283 |title=History of Civilizations of Central Asia: The Crossroads of Civilizations, A.D. 250 to 750 |date=1996 |publisher=UNESCO Publishing |isbn=978-92-3-103211-0 |language=en |access-date=2021-12-11 |archive-date=2021-08-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210814100317/https://books.google.com/books?id=883OZBe2sMYC&pg=PA283 |dead-url=no }}</ref>{{rp|283–}}塔里木盆地在语言学上的突厥化到11世纪末基本完成了。<ref name="Akiner2013">{{Cite book |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=udjWAQAAQBAJ&pg=PA71 |title=Cultural Change and Continuity in Central Asia |date=2013 |publisher=Routledge |isbn=978-1-136-15034-0 |editor-last=Akiner |editor-first=Shirin |location=London |language=en |access-date=2021-12-11 |archive-date=2020-12-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201206020748/https://books.google.com/books?id=udjWAQAAQBAJ&pg=PA71 |dead-url=no }}</ref>{{rp|71–}}

==系属分类 ==
于阗语和图木舒克语十分接近[[东伊朗语支|东伊朗语支]]。<ref>{{Cite book |last=Emmerick |first=Ronald |title=The Iranian Languages |date=2009 |publisher=Routledge |editor-last=Windfuhr |editor-first=Gernot |location=London |chapter=Khotanese and Tumshuqese}}</ref>{{rp|377–415}}

==文本==
[[File:Dandan_Uiliq_Khotanese_ms_British_Library_Khot_4-1.jpeg|thumb]]出土的[[于阗语|于阗语]]手稿，现藏于大英博物馆。]]
除伊塞克石冢上一般被认为是于阗语的铭文外(也以[[佉卢文|佉卢文]]书写)，所有现存材料都来自和田或图木舒克。[[敦煌文献|敦煌文献]]中，于阗语有超过2300份文本，<ref>{{Cite web |last=Wilson |first=Lee |date=2015-01-26 |title=Preliminary Proposal to Encode the Khotanese Script |url=https://unicode.org/L2/L2015/15022-khotanese.pdf |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190614224436/http://www.unicode.org/L2/L2015/15022-khotanese.pdf |archive-date=2019-06-14 |access-date=2019-05-21 |language=en |via=unicode.org}}</ref>图木舒克语只有15份。<ref>{{Cite web |title=Brāhmī |url=http://www.iranicaonline.org/articles/brahmi-indian-script |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190517031654/http://www.iranicaonline.org/articles/brahmi-indian-script |archive-date=2019-05-17 |access-date=2019-05-21 |website=Encyclopaedia Iranica |language=en}}</ref>它们由[[H._W._贝利|H. W. 贝利]]破译。<ref>{{Cite web |title=Bailey, Harold Walter |url=http://www.iranicaonline.org/articles/bailey-harold-walter-1 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210814100318/https://iranicaonline.org/articles/bailey-harold-walter-1 |archive-date=2021-08-14 |access-date=2019-05-21 |website=Encyclopaedia Iranica |language=en}}</ref>最早的文献是约4世纪的，主要是宗教文献。例文见{{IDP|Or.6400/2.3}}。

